{"tid":674084,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇女仔出完軌可以若無其事咁返返去男朋友到","createTime":"2018-05-22T11:44:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T17:07:06.000Z","uid":86309,"like":49,"dislike":103,"uniUserReply":62,"replies":[{"pid":"ef045afdba5bd7a6f4dfcf92cc374d529fce0ad0","tid":674084,"uid":86309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:44:46.000Z","msg":"我同個女仔各自都有另外一半<br />\n早幾個月開始曖昧<br />\n（係我知道自己變左心之後我就同左我女朋友分手，因為我知道自己個心唔係佢度）<br />\n同個女仔後來都有扑過野（唔止一次）<br />\n而佢都有提及過佢同男朋友之間唔太愉快<br />\n曾經我以為我地可以起埋一齊<br />\n但最後佢話斬攬因為佢同佢男朋友一齊太耐經歷左太多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n然後過幾日係ig繼續放閃好似咩都無發生咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係好佩服點解個女仔可以出軌之後對住男朋友咩事都無<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5fdecb21160a922240e2cbcbfd08df7ecd76b6e5","tid":674084,"uid":37546,"like":43,"dislike":1,"score":42,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:46:43.000Z","msg":"G<br />\n物以類聚 人以群分"},{"pid":"30798fa7367b5447b2e1b808c21dc3d90a40c2dd","tid":674084,"uid":2419,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:47:06.000Z","msg":"雞"},{"pid":"cb92617684a662953ee29d1b33ca67243a2668f1","tid":674084,"uid":39370,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:47:22.000Z","msg":"好出奇呀"},{"pid":"f39de21286e96b4032d733c8c04af184226949f2","tid":674084,"uid":119810,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:47:46.000Z","msg":"男人都係咁啦"},{"pid":"e2def2afb1cda0473cb40ccda1c1bd99706542a3","tid":674084,"uid":86309,"like":4,"dislike":29,"score":-25,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2018-05-22T11:48:45.000Z","msg":"我自問對呢個女仔動左心我已經唔知點面對我女朋友<br />\n而個女仔竟然可以扑埋野然後話斬攬同返男朋友一齊<br />\n我都知道在於肉體上我無任何損失<br />\n但情感上我好佩服女仔有呢個能力<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e392a714bffd61e71c520dac328fa37ad3ca8fb","tid":674084,"uid":56097,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05